      "id": "CVE-2025-15568",
      "publishedDate": "2026-03-09T16:19:05.777Z",
      "lastModifiedDate": "2026-03-09T16:19:05.777Z",
      "description": "A command injection vulnerability was identified in the web module of Archer AXE75 v1.6/v1.0 router.  An authenticated attacker with adjacent-network access may be able to perform remote code execution (RCE) when the router is configured with sysmode=ap.  Successful exploitation results in root-level privileges and impacts confidentiality, integrity and availability of the device.\n\nThis issue affects Archer AXE75 v1.6/v1.0: through 1.3.2 Build 20250107.",
      "severity": "N/A",
      "references": [
